    ('HON-H 238', 'POLITICS AND COMMUNICATION', '12343', 'Class Status', 'TuTh Tuesday, Thursday 9:35 AM–12:05 PM', 'FX 121', 'Dawn Wisher', 2, NULL, 'Seminar', '3', 'HUTTON HONORS COLLEGE', ARRAY[]::TEXT[], 'Examines communication as a vehicle for conveying political opinion, for forging political identities, for testing political and public ideas, and for understanding how political actors differentiate themselves in the public arena.', ARRAY['IUB GenEd S&H credit
